@model CampusBookFlip.WebUI.Models.NewEmailTokenEmail
@{
    Layout = null;
}
To: @Model.To
From: @Model.From
Subject: @Model.Subject

Hello @Model.FirstName,

Our records show that you would like to start using @Model.NewEmail instead of @Model.OldEmail.

Please visit @(new System.UriBuilder(Request.Url.AbsoluteUri) { Path = Url.Action("RegisterNewEmail", "Account", new { token = Model.ConfirmationToken, secret = Model.SharedSecret }) }.ToString()) in order to confirm this email address. @Model.OldEmail will be used until you complete this step.

Thank you!